{"tid":1595582,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"『薪火post』BNO續期資訊(63) 先睇頭POST同DOC後先問問題之Join Q改咗名","createTime":"2019-09-26T06:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T06:57:31.000Z","uid":78143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfc49bf9f19a179e1287a3e90a96f183e713e85","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:31:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;請新入嚟嘅巴絲打睇完Google Docs後唔明先問問題&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;&darr;</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU/edit?pli=1#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU%2Fedit%3Fpli%3D1%23&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=fb7766f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU/edit?pli=1#</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBTLhja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBTLhja.jpg&h=c50729bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDrWjPU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDrWjPU.png&h=ef901a2b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如閣下想到英國工作，請搜尋 英倫扮工室 POST</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">依家正值新舊系統交接期，實際申請過程可能會同 doc &amp; 頭 post 所寫內容有出入，請各申請人根據申請時網頁及確認電郵提供嘅指示完成申請程序，唔好盲目跟隨現有 doc &amp; 頭 post 嘅內容</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">另外希望使用新系統申請嘅巴打可以喺 post 度分享返整個申請流程，以便巴打更新返份 doc</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後更新 : 2019年9月25日</strong>"},{"pid":"b855c05d773958c44098ffeafdc9088e057d7c62","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EUDETB6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEUDETB6.png&h=a1669403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ElAtJX7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FElAtJX7.png&h=9ceee922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n申請續領英國國民海外護照<br />\n<br />\n（不適用於身處英國本土人士續領。以下文件清單為香港續領而設。如你於香港及英國以外地方續領，文件的要求或者申請方式可能有所不同，你可以瀏覽英國政府網站查閱身處地之確實申請方法）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>身份證大法及SAR (Subject access request) 需在HMPO註銷舊護照 ( CANCEL PASSPORT ) 後方可繼續續領新護照</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>在預備好所需文件前切勿提交申請。</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">你的申請不會僅因遞交申請前欠缺副署的聲明書而被拒絕。</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">Application History 係 HMPO 公務員人手 Update 所以不要過份緊張</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">如不能提供副署、證明文件或填寫表格時有錯誤，請寫信解釋。</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請用黑筆簽署所有表格及新護照</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n詳情或申請流程請參閱以下由<strong>卡斐帕西飛</strong> &amp; <strong>郭藹明日香</strong>製作既doc，由連登會員 <strong>希魔</strong> 所更新，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一般既疑問應該係呢份doc度答哂大家</span>。睇完之後有問題嘅話歡迎提問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">續領BN(O)詳細google document:</span></span></strong>(有關單次使用的緊急護照申請方法包含在內)<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU/edit?pli=1#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU%2Fedit%3Fpli%3D1%23&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=fb7766f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sccskS5ZN9vRZveWFRS0vneBNO5Fk8csOKj3H2s3sdU/edit?pli=1#</a></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d605d1d8f715bf3a0e9a247e0877a4402a2220f7","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新系統簡易續期資訊 by 希魔</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後更新 : 2019年9月7日</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>HMPO申請護照網站</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/apply-renew-passport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fapply-renew-passport&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=3fdaaf33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/apply-renew-passport</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>HMPO WEBCHAT</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/passport-advice-line\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fpassport-advice-line&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=b00f8134\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/passport-advice-line</a><br />\n<br />\n如果對英文有閱讀問題者請到以下網站 : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/service/travel_document/apply_for_hksar_passport.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservice%2Ftravel_document%2Fapply_for_hksar_passport.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=9a11bdfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/service/travel_document/apply_for_hksar_passport.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新系統是沒有 declaration form 要列印 ( 如需要只有 countersign 表格要列印 )</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如無特別指明，所有身份證明文件皆需要以正本呈上 ( 不包括香港身份證 )，如以副本呈上，HMPO將保留呈上正本的權利 ( 不包括香港身份證 ) 。 如你持有英國護照以外尚未註銷的其他國家護照需要正本或彩色副本呈上。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請用黑筆簽署所有表格 ( 包括 countersign [ 副簽 ] 表格 )</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如非UKPA, UKPS, IPS or HMPO選右邊 OTHER ( 例如 Passport Office Hong Kong / HKG選Other) </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n正常方式 ( 2004年或以後簽發, 但不包括 LOST &amp; STOLEN )<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意!身分證大法使用者<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必須</span></strong>以LOST &amp; STOLEN申請</span><br />\n表示不需要 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">COUNTERSIGN [ 副簽 ] </span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDp648t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDp648t.png&h=ab0c9782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別方式 ( 2003年或以前簽發, 包括 LOST &amp; STOLEN )<br />\n表示需要 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">COUNTERSIGN [ 副簽 ] </span></strong> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNVNPz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNVNPz9.png&h=6ff905d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n選上面 ( FOR LOST &amp; STOLEN ONLY )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmZWwW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmZWwW1.png&h=0e5c3861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">致身分證大法申請人:</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意，如果你是遺失舊BNO或正在使用身份證大法<br />\n你必須先網上報失 -</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">選擇 No - I need to cancel it now</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">填寫基本報失資料後需要聯絡HMPO方可完成整個報失程序<br />\n有關流程參見<a href=\"https://lih.kg/hRcvKLX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/hRcvKLX</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">注意 : 以上的情況需要註銷舊護照後方可繼續續領新護照</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n及 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">PARENTS' DETAILS</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YZnLZY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YZnLZY.png&h=f0970e93&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;Were they married or in a civil partnership?&quot;<br />\n父母已經離婚選YES 及寫信解釋已離婚<br />\nCivil partnership 係uk野，並非香港野。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/civil-partnership-what-is-it-explained-heterosexual-same-sex-couples-marriage-benefits-a8419591.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Flife-style%2Fcivil-partnership-what-is-it-explained-heterosexual-same-sex-couples-marriage-benefits-a8419591.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=8b927edf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/civil-partnership-what-is-it-explained-heterosexual-same-sex-couples-marriage-benefits-a8419591.html</a><br />\n<br />\n舊護照資料 <strong>選填</strong> ( FOR LOST &amp; STOLEN ONLY )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9r9reW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9r9reW.png&h=e6fe874a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n付款之後會有位 download countersign [ 副簽 ] PDF<br />\n英國外申請人仕請用右下角(Paper Form)作副署<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kayvNo0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkayvNo0.png&h=11b30217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果出現以下版面<br />\n開始時揀錯英國本土續領<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrB5Bit.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrB5Bit.png&h=bf596641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所需文件 CHECKLIST : <br />\n<br />\n香港身份證彩色副本 ( 雙面 )<br />\n舊 BNO 護照 ( 如有 )<br />\n地址證明 [ 英文 ] <br />\nCountersign [ 副簽 ] 表格 ( 如需要 )<br />\nCertificate of Registration - BDTC ( 如需要 )<br />\nParents' Details 證明文件 ( 如需要 )<br />\n未註銷的其他國家護照正本或彩色副本 ( 如需要 )<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">你的申請不會僅因遞交申請前欠缺副署的聲明書而被拒絕。</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n郵件追查<br />\n<br />\n香港郵政郵件追查網址<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/mail_tracking/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk%2Ftc%2Fmail_tracking%2Findex.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=99ef7c0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/mail_tracking/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\nRoyal Mail Track and Trace<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.royalmail.com/track-your-item#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalmail.com%2Ftrack-your-item%23%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=746e7ab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.royalmail.com/track-your-item#/</a><br />\n<br />\nDHL Track System<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dhl.com.hk/en/express/tracking.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dhl.com.hk%2Fen%2Fexpress%2Ftracking.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=74bcea18\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dhl.com.hk/en/express/tracking.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n處理情況<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSbYjmp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSbYjmp.jpg&h=95c25914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.passport.service.gov.uk/track\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passport.service.gov.uk%2Ftrack&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=b6c1f689\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.passport.service.gov.uk/track</a><br />\n<br />\n最後HMPO寄出護照及證明文件後會照你選擇的通信方法 ( Email 或電話號碼 )送出護照及證明文件的追蹤號碼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPiPAKv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPiPAKv.png&h=6e76f0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新護照</span></strong><br />\n收到新護照請檢查個人資料是否正確無誤<br />\n<br />\n如有個人資料錯誤或沒有歸還證明文件，請用 Webchat 聯絡 HMPO :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/passport-advice-line\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fpassport-advice-line&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=b00f8134\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/passport-advice-line</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請用黑筆簽署新護照</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nNormal Observations : <br />\n<br />\nBefore Brexit<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3pu3nW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3pu3nW.jpg&h=62780e86&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAfter Brexit<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxZbxde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxZbxde.jpg&h=c86ebd95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要有齊三段，次序不會有影響。"},{"pid":"7c0de3b85163911468119c7d5ecdd30fbe4b2296","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我不知道或忘記了是否擁有BN(O)身份，有辧法查詢嗎？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n請先用身份證大法檢查，之後才用SAR (Subject access request)。<br />\n<br />\n身份證大法及SAR (Subject access request) 需在HMPO註銷舊護照 ( CANCEL PASSPORT ) 後方可繼續續領新護照。<br />\n<br />\n1. 身份證大法<br />\n<br />\n鳴謝高登會員 eclass 提供以下方法。<br />\n<br />\n合符以下<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有</strong></span>條件基本上可以肯定你有過BNO身份：<br />\n- 1997年7月1日前未滿11歲<br />\n- 身份證首次簽發日期為(06-97)或之前<br />\n- 香港出世而且出世紙寫有'Established'<br />\n<br />\n<strong>合符以上<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有</strong></span>條件，要向 HMPO 作 REPORT LOST PASSPORT ，需在HMPO註銷舊護照 ( CANCEL PASSPORT ) 後方可繼續續領新護照。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下方法只適用1986年或之後在香港出生，而且出生時已經是永久性居民 (請參考出世紙最後一格必須寫明 'established')。</strong><br />\n<br />\n你只能夠直接向HMPO遞交護照申請並繳付相關付用，HMPO才會對你的英國國籍作出審查。請留意如果最終HMPO發現你是沒有任何英國國籍身份，所繳交的申請費用不會退還。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你於1997年7月前未滿11歲並且未持有11歲－17歲人士香港永久性居民身份證或你肯定自己曾經持有一張沒有相片的11歲以下人士兒童身份證的話，請留意：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9Eu3i0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9Eu3i0.png&h=7732f4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實如果你在<strong>1997年7月(同年1月1日至6月30日出生者則為同年9月)前未滿十一歲並曾領取十一歲以下兒童身份證的話</strong>，由於以往<strong>十一歲以下的人士申請BN(O)護照必須同時申請十一歲以下人士兒童身份證</strong>，這是強制性的，所以是可以靠你的身份證上面的首次登記身份證的月份和年份來判斷是否擁有BN(O)身份。 這項措施旨在於確保持有英國國民(海外)身份的人士在主權移交後繼續有返回香港的權利，以使護照內「The holder of this passport has Hong Kong permanent identity card number (XYZ) which states that the holder has the right of abode in Hong Kong.」條文有效。補充一點，十一歲以下人士兒童身份證是沒有相片的。<br />\n<br />\n首次登記身份證的月份和年份在你的身份證的簽發日期一欄，以括號包住。 如果該<strong>日期為06-97或之前(97年1月1日至97年6月30日或之前出生者為09-97或之前)</strong>，你有很大機會擁有BN(O)身份。<br />\n<br />\n請留意此方法並不能完全確定你是否曾經擁有BN(O)身份，因為當年11歲以下人士申請香港身份證明書(CI,  Certificate of Identity) 如從未擁有香港身份證者均會獲同時簽發11歲以下人士身份證，所以請你自行決定最終是否遞交申請。<br />\n<br />\n如果你無法找出舊的BN(O)護照但只持有一本接近主權移交前簽發的身份證明書，可能意味着你並沒有英國國民(海外)身份。<br />\n<br />\n如果是 Include Child 情況，你都會曾領取十一歲以下兒童身份證。<br />\n申請將會以 First Passport 情況 ( 特別方式 ) 處理。<br />\n需要 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">COUNTERSIGN</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isxXsRD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FisxXsRD.jpg&h=7c3d84ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxZOzwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxZOzwH.jpg&h=59d88c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9rdLDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9rdLDo.jpg&h=b1dbcfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. SAR (Subject access request)<br />\n<br />\n直接向英國提出 SAR (Subject access request)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主權移交時超過11歲或不清楚閣下是否有英國國籍請參考以下方法直接向英國提出SAR (Subject access request)<br />\n查詢英國政府是否有你英國國籍 ( 包括BNO ) 的記錄<br />\n<br />\n如閣下是 INCLUDE CHILD ，是不會有英國護照 ( 包括BNO ) 的記錄。<br />\n<br />\n&rdquo;If you wish to know if you have had any passport in the past, you will need to send a SAR (Subject access request). This will give you information you require.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Please send your request to the following email address: DPA.Queries@hmpo.gov.uk&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Please provide your full name and date of birth, also your country of birth. You will need to state exactly what information it is you are required to provide.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"a90927473291e7c49355a2bf8b598380276a86e5","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:32:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">身份證明文件</span><br />\n<br />\n核證副本<br />\n<br />\n出 生 登 記 記 項 核 證 副 本<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/birth-death/Application_for_Search_of_Birth_Records_and_Certified_Copy_of_Birth_Entry.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservices%2Fbirth-death%2FApplication_for_Search_of_Birth_Records_and_Certified_Copy_of_Birth_Entry.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=7fb6ee87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/birth-death/Application_for_Search_of_Birth_Records_and_Certified_Copy_of_Birth_Entry.html</a><br />\n<br />\n結 婚 證 書 核 證 副 本<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/marriage/Searching_Marriage_Records_and_Certified_Copy_of_Marriage_Entry.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservices%2Fmarriage%2FSearching_Marriage_Records_and_Certified_Copy_of_Marriage_Entry.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=d5d61559\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/marriage/Searching_Marriage_Records_and_Certified_Copy_of_Marriage_Entry.html</a><br />\n<br />\n正本或影印本喺手所以做特定查冊<br />\n<br />\n上網填完form俾錢之後大概2個禮拜可以去返生死註冊處同婚姻登記處攞核證副本<br />\n<br />\n如果資料唔齊可能要一般查冊<br />\n<br />\n登 記 事 項 證 明 書<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/hkid/apply_cert.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservices%2Fhkid%2Fapply_cert.html&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=af875d88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/hkid/apply_cert.html</a><br />\n<br />\n宣誓樣本<br />\n<br />\n地址證明<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/dra/Statutory%20Declaration.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fdra%2FStatutory%2520Declaration.pdf&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=c8d58a6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/dra/Statutory%20Declaration.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"e2ba1f7908f62a844e11f323c9d4d701cac480ce","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/edModEo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FedModEo.png&h=098c32af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bnohk.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnohk.org&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=3e987ce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnohk.org</a> <br />\n<br />\n由我地<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Pf6rbbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPf6rbbz.gif&h=bd85283f&s={SIZE}\" />會員 (殘酷的小賓周, leChronique,  あの子大好き) 製成既BNO續期資訊網站 <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xXepk1M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxXepk1M.gif&h=956c926e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xXepk1M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxXepk1M.gif&h=956c926e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xXepk1M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxXepk1M.gif&h=956c926e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xXepk1M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxXepk1M.gif&h=956c926e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05656d086bc73058eab05498e349dade536b211e","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HMPO官方指引（適用於香港申請）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n從香港申請英國國民海外（British National Overseas (BNO)）護照（廣東話／英文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/how-to-apply-for-a-british-national-overseas-passport-from-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fhow-to-apply-for-a-british-national-overseas-passport-from-hong-kong&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=41229542\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/how-to-apply-for-a-british-national-overseas-passport-from-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n於英國以外地方申請護照指南（網上申請適用）(英文)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/254490/OS_OL_Guidance_10.13.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F254490%2FOS_OL_Guidance_10.13.pdf&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=7ce5fda0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/254490/OS_OL_Guidance_10.13.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n於英國以外地方申請護照的所需證明文件 (英文)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/342795/Supportingdocs2AUG2014.PDF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F342795%2FSupportingdocs2AUG2014.PDF&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=87d6e4e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/342795/Supportingdocs2AUG2014.PDF</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外交及聯邦事務部的旅遊建議</span></span><br />\n<br />\n出發前往他國旅遊前，請先參考外交及聯邦事務部有否對你前往的目的地發出任何建議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fforeign-travel-advice&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=d668b107\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice</a><br />\n<br />\nfacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fcotravel/?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffcotravel%2F%3Ffref%3Dts&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=2b68a4e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fcotravel/?fref=ts</a><br />\n<br />\ntwitter <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fcotravel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffcotravel&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=9325ced6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fcotravel</a><br />\n<br />\nBNO 續期資訊網站 by 殘酷的小賓周 leChronique あの子大好き (LIHKG會員<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Pf6rbbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPf6rbbz.gif&h=bd85283f&s={SIZE}\" />) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bnohk.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnohk.org&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=3e987ce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnohk.org</a><br />\n<br />\n臺灣旅行英國國民（海外）護照及特區護照問題<br />\n<br />\n中華民國<br />\n<br />\n香港澳門關係條例<br />\n<br />\n第四條 本條例所稱香港居民，指具有香港永久居留資格，且未持有英國國民（海外）護照或香港護照以外之旅行證照者。<br />\n<br />\n本條例所稱澳門居民，指具有澳門永久居留資格，且未持有澳門護照以外之旅行證照或雖持有葡萄牙護照但係於葡萄牙結束治理前於澳門取得者。<br />\n<br />\n前二項香港或澳門居民，如於香港或澳門分別於英國及葡萄牙結束其治理前，取得華僑身分者及其符合中華民國國籍取得要件之配偶及子女，在本條例施行前之既有權益，應予以維護。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mac.gov.tw/cp.aspx?n=24F1371BF3738F96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mac.gov.tw%2Fcp.aspx%3Fn%3D24F1371BF3738F96&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=bae4bdbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mac.gov.tw/cp.aspx?n=24F1371BF3738F96</a>"},{"pid":"656489eb6c62639e493e482a3622d080c30929d5","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">FAQ 常見問題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以下問題皆為巴打們列出最常見問題而且已經填哂答案，而呢d答案係上面個份google doc入面已經講齊哂，如果你問以下問題而被屌，唔好問點解。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n約法三章先 <br />\n有幾個情況既問題各位一定唔好答 <br />\n1. 過左期十年駛唔駛副簽? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><del>唔係過左期幾多年就一定要副署，係睇你個樣仲可唔可以從你既護照入面認出黎，認得出就唔使，認唔出就要。</del>你份declaration form 有印到副署部份就要副署，無印到就唔使。</span><br />\n2. 影相可唔可以戴眼鏡影? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以，但你要確保你既眼鏡唔會遮住你對眼同唔會反光。</span><br />\n3. 張相既背景要咩色? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">白色或灰色</span><br />\n4. 去旅行用BNO寫咩國籍? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">British National (Overseas) 或 BNO 或 British 或 GBN</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"> 如果你係online check-in 或需要係網上揀國籍嘅話，請有得揀BN(O)時優先揀BN(O)，無就揀UK/GB/British/Great Britain/任何代表英國嘅文字。</span><br />\n5. 舊護照係bb相，續唔續到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (紅色封面BNO係BB相咪續到囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Why not?</span><br />\n6. 身份證要影兩面定單面? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩面</span><br />\n7. 特衰要影邊幾頁? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由頭影到落尾，包括封面、個人資料頁、空白頁、有印既頁、有visa既頁、說明頁，你本護照有幾多頁，就印哂幾多頁。</span><br />\n8. 搵到本BNO剪左角，仲續唔續到? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">搵到本BNO剪左角，仲續唔續到? </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正常情況: 你應該仲有一本未剪角既，搵清楚啲，搵唔到就以 lost passport 處理</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">特殊情況: 有可能係申請特衰時香港嘅公務員手誤剪咗，當 damaged passport 處理</span><br />\n9. 點解地址少左行? 係唔係搞錯左? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正常</span><br />\n10. 無住址證明，點好? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最細既BN(O) holder都18歲，點可能無，咪玩啦</span><br />\n11. 點解DHL份件得本新BNO? 我本舊證呢? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你寄左既文件、舊護照會同新護照分開兩份速遞寄畀你</span><br />\n12. 呢本野續唔續到 (BDTC) <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">BDTC全部已經係1997年7月1日失效，你應該再搵下屋企有無另外一本BNO護照</span><br />\n13. 副簽人係咪可以係親戚? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以</span><br />\n14. 轉左dispatched 之後幾時收到？ <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">等SMS，會答你寄時到</span><br />\n15. 點樣寄去英國？幾錢？ <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">空郵掛號200g $ 50起，睇你份野最後重量而定<br />\nspeedpost 200g $225 大約2-6個工作日寄到<br />\n郵局寄Speedpost有紙文件套免費拎寄之前上網入資料平$10<br />\nDHL $ 自己打上去hotline問價 24003388</span>"},{"pid":"8699f158ee05454f3a73b25ae7bd397cab528de6","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:33:35.000Z","msg":"16. 續個陣個簽名可唔可以簽中文 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你簽乜都得</span><br />\n17. 有sar果本仲續唔續得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Why not?</span> <br />\n18. 點知自己細個有無申請過 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">畀錢申請一次就知</span><br />\n19. 老豆老母本BNO有我個名申唔申請到? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Why not?</span><br />\n20. 有無人試過有本火車頭都扮無，唔印就照申請? <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解要扮無？有就印，無就唔使印。</span><br />\n21. 有冇人試過一個speed post 寄兩份或以上申請係成功？ <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">成功例子：網上一次過交兩份申請(打完一個比錢前可以繼續加申請)，一齊比錢一齊寄一齊dispatch一齊收到</span><br />\n22.我搵唔到人副署，有無巴打可以幫到手？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無，我地呢度無人識你兩年或以上，全部都無資格做你副署人。</span><br />\n23. 如果續個陣想加個英文名上去駛唔駛副簽?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">凡事無絕對，怕就揀change to an existing passport搵人簽埋，唔怕既就唔簽寄左先，HMPO覺得你要既就自然有人會搵你。叫你簽返</span><br />\n24. 可唔可以寄本正本特衰比佢 (過期/未過期) <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以 </span><br />\n25.用過廁板去台灣，可唔可以轉 BNO?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">喺台灣眼中，只要你符合港澳關係條例第四條香港居民嘅定義，無論你拎廁板定係 BNO 入境都一樣係當香港居民處理，台灣關員係唔應該以持雙重國籍為由拒絕手持 BNO 嘅香港居民入境，無論你有冇曾經用過廁板入境台灣都係咁話注意: 以上唔適用於廁板或BNO 以外嘅任何外國國籍</span><br />\n26.要幾耐先完成申請?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">視乎case 複雜程度+你比幾多文件人處理</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">個個officer 處理需時都唔同....但呢到case大部份2weeks 內會由MHPO收到全部所需文件處理申請去到dispatched</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">OR 官方答案: 5星期</span><br />\n27. 外地遺失BNO餘下行程是否必須取消並立即返港?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">BNO其中的一個好處是方便持有人在遺失原有BNO護照情況下在英國駐外使領館迅速補領緊急護照。雖然是一本緊急護照，但並非降格成一本緊急「旅行證」。緊急護照有效期最長為一年，持照人仍然可免簽證出入境以下國家：<br />\n亞太：泰國、日本、韓國、星加坡、澳洲(ETA)；<br />\n歐洲：全歐盟境內、冰島、瑞士、挪威、列支敦士登、摩納哥、塞爾維亞、黑山、波斯尼亞、阿爾巴尼亞、摩爾多瓦、馬其頓；<br />\n非洲：摩洛哥、突尼西亞、南非；<br />\n美洲：加拿大(ETA)、墨西哥、哥倫比亞、委內瑞拉、厄瓜多爾、秘魯、智利、玻利維亞、巴西、巴拉圭、烏拉圭、巴拿馬、哥斯達黎加；<br />\n特區護照持有人在外地遺失護照，因中國駐外使館不能簽發特區護照，故只可在當地申請「中國旅行證」作為臨時證件。而因為「中國旅行證」並非特區護照，只能作返回中國或原居地用。大部份國家並不接受以此證件作過境或辦理第三國簽證用，倘若在第一個國家已經遺失特區護照，餘下行程亦只能放棄，直接返港或回原居地。若同時遺失特區護照及香港永久居民身分證，當事人只可向中國駐當地使領館申請「入境身份陳述書」直接返港。</span><br />\n28. 如果成功續領新BNO，而美國簽證仍在特區護照點算?<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk_zh/hk-gen-faq.asp#qlistgen8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ustraveldocs.com%2Fhk_zh%2Fhk-gen-faq.asp%23qlistgen8&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=9f64f69b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk_zh/hk-gen-faq.asp#qlistgen8</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">問 8. 我的護照已過期，但美國簽證仍有效。我需要申請新簽證嗎？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果旅客持有一本有效但未附上美國簽證的香港特別行政區護照, 及一本附上有效美國簽證的過期英國國民(海外)護照前往美國, 或者反之亦言, 兩者在 技術上皆是可行的; 但請留意, 他/她在入境口岸面見移民官員時可能會有阻滯。或者, 為避免產生問題及阻滯, 他/她可以申請新的簽證在新的香港特別行政區護照/新的英國國民(海外)護照上。因為這是新的申請, 所以必須繳交不可退還的申請費用。當他/她申請時, 無論他/她是否獲發新簽證, 任何相同類別的簽證都會被註銷。</span><br />\n29. 我使用BNO外遊若同行配偶/子女並非英籍(例如只有特區護照)，遇上事故英國領事館會一同協助他們嗎?<br />\n<a href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/781770/Support_for_British_Nationals_Abroad_Main_Guide.pdf#page=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F781770%2FSupport_for_British_Nationals_Abroad_Main_Guide.pdf%23page%3D7&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=5c62792d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/781770/Support_for_British_Nationals_Abroad_Main_Guide.pdf#page=7</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">第25頁<br />\n<strong>Who we can help in a crisis</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&gt; In certain circumstances, family members of British nationals (spouse/partner and dependent children aged 18 years and under only &ndash; we cannot assist other family members).<br />\n特別情況下，求助者的伴侶/配偶及子女(只限18歲或以下)都會得到得到英國領事館協助，但其他非英籍親友不會得到協助</span><br />\n30. 我不清楚我是否有過BN(O)身份，有方法查詢?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1997年7月1日前未滿11歲者可以使用「身分證大法」得知你是否BN(O):<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">合符以下條件基本上可以肯定你有過BNO身份：\n- 1997年7月1日前未滿11歲\n- 身份證上首次簽發日期為(06-97)或之前*\n- 香港出世而且出世紙寫有'Established'</code></pre><br />\n*只需查看現時身分證即可<br />\n全中以上三項條件代表你父母曾經在主權移交前代你申請過BNO<br />\n不符合以上全部條件並不代表你沒有過BNO身份<br />\n詳細身分證大法資訊請參閱Doc有關該大法部份</span><br />\n<br />\n主權移交時超過11歲請參考以下方法直接向英國提出SAR<br />\n查詢英國政府是否有你BNO的記錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/igfiMGX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/igfiMGX</a>"},{"pid":"ad30e47f3dda9d2268783b8320df4b11584e6cc1","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">副署人問題 郭藹明日香(即酸民治日鮮) 提供 </span> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Pf6rbbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPf6rbbz.gif&h=bd85283f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首選：完全跟從指引做 <br />\n<br />\n次選：符合國籍要求，持有效符合國籍嘅護照，但返嘅工唔屬佢列明嘅專業人士。（HMPO嗰張list其實只係例子，無話唔跟一定唔得） <br />\n<br />\n再次選：副署人為英國國民或愛爾蘭公民但護照已遺失或過期，返緊list有嘅專業人士或有張list所要求嘅專業資格。 <br />\n<br />\n再再次選：副署人為英國國民或愛爾蘭公民但護照已遺失或過期，但返嘅工唔屬佢列明嘅專業人士。（HMPO嗰張list其實只係例子，無話唔跟一定唔得） <br />\n<br />\n再再再次選：副署人為英聯邦公民、歐盟國民、美國公民但護照已遺失或過期返緊list有嘅專業人士或有張list所要求嘅專業資格。 <br />\n<br />\n再再再再次選：副署人為英聯邦公民、歐盟國民、美國公民，但返嘅工唔屬佢列明嘅專業人士。（HMPO嗰張list其實只係例子，無話唔跟一定唔得） <br />\n<br />\n再再再再再次選：不符合國籍條件，只有本地國家有效護照，返緊list有嘅專業人士或有張list所要求嘅專業資格。 <br />\n<br />\n再再再再再再次選：不符合國籍條件，只有本地國家有效護照，但返嘅工唔屬佢列明嘅專業人士。（HMPO嗰張list其實只係例子，無話唔跟一定唔得） <br />\n<br />\n我唔保證你揀跟上面次選項目做HMPO唔會要求你搵另一位合資格嘅副署人，但係你應該搵一位係你身邊最能接近合符要求嘅副署人為你簽署。 <br />\n<br />\n但無論如何，認識兩年以上呢個條件係最基本，因為副署人嘅目的係證實該相片嘅人嘅樣貌係護照持有人，如果嗰個人識唔夠你兩年，憑乜嘢幫你做副署人？ <br />\n<br />\n我諗咁樣寫嘅話，你哋會有動力啲搵副署人，但係我再講多次你搵唔到首選級嘅副署人就會有風險，所以自行衡量啦。<br />\n<br />\n**以上例子係現有BN(O)持有人談及過往申請並如果申請人限時內無提交副署可能申請失敗。BN(O)嘅審批鬆緊可以急升可以急跌申請人或會蒙受申請失敗嘅全盤損失，而過往表現並非未來表現嘅指標，所以申請前請參讀HMPO嘅文件作出風險評估，同埋尋求專家嘅意見。"},{"pid":"6dc390cd456c4c73fb5c8f09f510b3e83d9606ea","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"Place of birth 一覽<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eFD1GC0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeFD1GC0.jpg&h=4b24288f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WgThQ8n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWgThQ8n.jpg&h=787579e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iyDucxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiyDucxF.jpg&h=a7a48e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CiUMWuL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCiUMWuL.png&h=75ee50f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bCeXtw1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbCeXtw1.jpg&h=a778a60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tIaJRMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtIaJRMC.png&h=9c7f56ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最新</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gCNH4fC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgCNH4fC.png&h=5267bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e62e1fa7e6346933985682b548fb11b633bc4e","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RLZEC8k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRLZEC8k.png&h=135d0a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GSoMUax.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGSoMUax.png&h=5207bbe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HQKhaDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHQKhaDh.png&h=54d5026d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gJqXo54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgJqXo54.png&h=b10743ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n改返左做岩既版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2018年數字</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jujO6Pj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjujO6Pj.png&h=cfea1b89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IxYt7Gi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIxYt7Gi.png&h=f8d34d3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4741fbfd815e74ced2b11cb0ec3d962b58a2ae2c","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NU6zXMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNU6zXMK.jpg&h=12f0ac5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我的護照已過期、遺失或損毀，但我急需護照出行，我可以怎辦？<br />\n<br />\n你可以選擇直接申請單次緊急護照(Emergency Travel Document, ETD)，費用為1,100港幣。ETD最多可使用進出5個國家，但請先自行檢查目的地國家是否接受ETD。另外ETD用完是需要交回領事館。<br />\n<br />\n請注意，緊急護照不論任何原因，包括普通旅行，只要你當時沒有可用的護照均可申請，適合「大頭蝦」忘記在預訂酒店及機票前檢查護照有效期的你申請。請留意，<span style=\"color: red;\">護照過期超過十年或以上者可能無法申請辦理緊急護照</span>，如果你是此類人士，請事先於辧公時間內致電英國駐香港總領事或向你身在地的英國大使館、高級專員公署或領事館查詢。<br />\n<br />\n需要文件：<br />\n-已填妥之緊急旅遊證件申請表格<br />\n-證件相2張 (白底BNO相)<br />\n-旅行詳細行程 (旅行詳細會印在ETD上，如你要更改目的地，你需要再APPLY一次)<br />\n-身分證<br />\n-預機約票同酒店紀錄證明<br />\n-過期BNO 護照正本<br />\n-警署的報失護照證明（如遺失護照）<br />\n<br />\n步驟： <br />\n1.先於網上下載及填好emergency passport申請表格<br />\n2.帶齊文件儘早到金鐘英國駐港領事館<br />\n3.於保安部放低手機，講低想申請emergency Passport<br />\n4.保安會帶你去見領事館人員<br />\n5.向領事館人員出示已填妥之emergency passport申請表格、證件相、旅行詳細行程、身分證、預機約票同酒店紀錄證明及過期BNO 護照正本<br />\n6.等待領事館人員批核，成功後收申請費用及通知領取時間"},{"pid":"ec6d5337e7347caeb61076761c5c1fcd3854ad31","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">BNO VISA checking</span></strong></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bnovisa.tk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbnovisa.tk%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=df83f097\" target=\"_blank\">http://bnovisa.tk/</a><br />\n<br />\n由殘酷的小賓周提供 <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Pf6rbbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPf6rbbz.gif&h=bd85283f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7845a653e11ad0ee7d657d2fa4c16866cf6ef59","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"成日見到好多人笑續BNO貴<br />\n我係到諗: 係外國護照特別貴,定支國護照特別平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出於求真search過<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.passport-collector.com/passport-fees-around-world-2018-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passport-collector.com%2Fpassport-fees-around-world-2018-2%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=01b32044\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.passport-collector.com/passport-fees-around-world-2018-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n成人標準護照,計美金: (部分)<br />\n英國 90<br />\n澳洲 212<br />\n加拿大 128<br />\n蝗 29<br />\n特衰 32<br />\n古巴 100 (美國續375)<br />\n芬蘭 50 (5年有效期,10年=100)<br />\n法國 90<br />\n德國 66<br />\n以色列 75<br />\n意大利 135<br />\n日本 115<br />\n荷蘭 78<br />\n挪威 50<br />\n葡萄牙 60<br />\n南韓 50<br />\n俄 42<br />\n坡 59 (5年有效期,10年=118)<br />\n西班牙 25<br />\n瑞典 40<br />\n瑞士 140<br />\n土耳其 268 (5年有效期,10年536)<br />\n美國 110<br />\n<br />\n結論: 根本就係共國頂爛市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,要國藉欄唔要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ing Chinese ,特別係發達國家國藉,就要預左貴(除非連登好多西班牙藉,笑埋特衰都仲得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有又話乜春血濃於水,點解特衰要收得貴過蝗,講到尾又係當香港人水魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,又要亂咁派d特衰比權貴,整臭哂聲譽<br />\n<br />\n(擅自偷post者全家萬碎萬碎萬萬碎,生生世世都係中國窮人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\nBy ItsOver9000 <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Pf6rbbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPf6rbbz.gif&h=bd85283f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8SuCcZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW8SuCcZ.gif&h=fc7ca95e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8SuCcZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW8SuCcZ.gif&h=fc7ca95e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8SuCcZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW8SuCcZ.gif&h=fc7ca95e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8SuCcZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW8SuCcZ.gif&h=fc7ca95e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"452100c14188eeb0477051e607e94cd45e150199","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:34:55.000Z","msg":"CNO使用實例:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8ERgYiG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8ERgYiG.png&h=e081890d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBy 9394+689<br />\n<br />\nBNO使用實例:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FSsUatp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFSsUatp.png&h=8fa64e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBy 9394+689 <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Pf6rbbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPf6rbbz.gif&h=bd85283f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8SuCcZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW8SuCcZ.gif&h=fc7ca95e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8SuCcZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW8SuCcZ.gif&h=fc7ca95e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8SuCcZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW8SuCcZ.gif&h=fc7ca95e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W8SuCcZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW8SuCcZ.gif&h=fc7ca95e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人使用中國大使館服務實例，不負所望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n为什么中国驻外使领馆的服务评价会这么差？ - 李逍遙的回答 - 知乎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/28535919/answer/66015878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F28535919%2Fanswer%2F66015878&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=c4f27d70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/28535919/answer/66015878</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAfbZ4u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAfbZ4u.png&h=1e63390e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1eb79a20ad430a530b4dacf4c09795867ec36c91","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英倫扮工室 VISA</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如閣下想到英國工作，請搜尋 英倫扮工室 POST</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nThe first step to UK is to read through all the information provided (google it yourself if necessary)<br />\nas some British might not even know how to do their job (HR are all the same around the globe)<br />\n<br />\nVisa<br />\n<br />\nTier 5 (Youth Mobility Scheme) visa - Also known as working holiday<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tier-5-youth-mobility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ftier-5-youth-mobility&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=05af7cbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/tier-5-youth-mobility</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/forumdisplay.php?f=300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backpackers.com.tw%2Fforum%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ff%3D300&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=2be18711\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/forumdisplay.php?f=300</a><br />\nBNO &gt;&gt; HKSAR<br />\nIf you&rsquo;re applying this visa using HKSAR passport. You need to be sponsored with an annual quota of 1000.<br />\n<br />\nTier 2 (General - Working)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tier-2-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ftier-2-general&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=746d24f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/tier-2-general</a><br />\n<br />\nFor Settlement - Permanent Residence/Indefinite Leave to Remain (ILR)<br />\nOption 1<br />\nIf you have been living in UK for 10 years and met certain requirements<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/long-residence/eligibility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Flong-residence%2Feligibility&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6585ff74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/long-residence/eligibility</a><br />\nOption 2<br />\nIf you have been living and working (under Tier 2) in the UK for 5 years and met certain requirements<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/settle-in-the-uk/y/you-have-a-work-visa/tier-2-general-visa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fsettle-in-the-uk%2Fy%2Fyou-have-a-work-visa%2Ftier-2-general-visa&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=984aa48c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/settle-in-the-uk/y/you-have-a-work-visa/tier-2-general-visa</a><br />\n<br />\nHousing<br />\n<a href=\"http://Rightmove.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FRightmove.com&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=65bab416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Rightmove.com</a><br />\n<br />\nDriving<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/apply-first-provisional-driving-licence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fapply-first-provisional-driving-licence&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=032e2790\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/apply-first-provisional-driving-licence</a><br />\nExchange your driving licence<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/dvlaforms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fdvlaforms&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4036db08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/dvlaforms</a><br />\n<br />\nLiving Cost<br />\nLondon/Cambridge - Same as Hong Kong<br />\nOutside the above metropolitan area, and the rest of the UK - cheaper than Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 1:<br />\nI need English C2 level to get a job.<br />\nNope you don't, B2 is doable.<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 2:<br />\nA smaller firm is more likely to help with visa issues.<br />\nNo, not likely at all.<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 3:<br />\nTier 5 switch to Tier 2?<br />\nIt is possible but not going to be easy.<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 4:<br />\nTier 4 to Tier 2?<br />\nPreparing it when you are in year 2.<br />\n<br />\nFAQ 5:<br />\nTier 2/4/5 to settlement immediately?<br />\nDefinitively possible if you are a single girl, or boy?<br />\nLevae your tg/ig here with your sexual orientation and a picture. Our 手足 will contact you shortly.<br />\n<br />\nbackup<br />\n<a href=\"https://new.reddit.com/r/UKHKSkiver/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.reddit.com%2Fr%2FUKHKSkiver%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=2dd2c3df\" target=\"_blank\">https://new.reddit.com/r/UKHKSkiver/</a><br />\n<br />\ninfo<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/forumdisplay.php?f=300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backpackers.com.tw%2Fforum%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ff%3D300&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=2be18711\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/forumdisplay.php?f=300</a>"},{"pid":"5e0412951376bbc9f2fc486af6c05d29dd5a6511","tid":1595582,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"『薪火post』BNO續期資訊(64) 先睇頭POST同DOC後先問問題之Join Q改咗名<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595594\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595594</a>"},{"pid":"44d696ee6c30df124cbb8e68cc6718eb97a8e63b","tid":1595582,"uid":21461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:57:31.00